KZN Education MEC Kwazi Mshengu gives details on the fatal incident. Courtesy #DStv403 DURBAN - A grade eight pupil has been stabbed to death at a school in Ulundi, KwaZulu-Natal. The incident happened at Ekudubeni Secondary School on Friday. READ: Pupil stabbed to death at Sebokeng school laid to rest Reports suggest that the pupil was stabbed by a fellow pupil.